The paper deals with deep learning approaches to segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new method for learning pixel-wise representations, which is a machine learning task (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper uses a CRF, which is a common tool in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and similarity scores (cs.IR).
